===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|sleep|lang=enm}}, {{term|sleepe|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|slæp|slǣp|sleep|sc=Latinx|lang=ang}}, from {{proto|Germanic|slaepaz}}.  Cognate with {{etyl|nl|-}} {{term|slaap|lang=nl}}, {{etyl|de|-}} {{term|Schlaf|lang=de}}.

